## Task on AWS:

AES new account
Create a new account and make sure you get notifications if you waste too much money.
Create a new AWS Accout
Here are some important details to notice:
	- One email address per aws account
	- This address will be linked to the AWS root account
	- Choose basic support plan (see here for more details)
So follow these instruction to create your new account.
Configure a Billing Alarm
A billing alarm will send you an email notification if you spend too much money on AWS.
Here are some notes:
	- The alarm is based on the aws cloudwatch service, this is the service that discovers the metrics that sets the alarm.
	- The email notification is created by SNS (Simple Notification Service), a service that is used to send email messages and SMS messages.
	- Use this link to configure the billing alarm.
